title: Read and Write Archive File Formats

questions.question: You must always use a single merged feature type to read from an archive file format.
Which case would benefit from writing to an archive file format?
options: You need to write to a database.
Your workspace concludes by appending records to an Esri geodatabase feature class.
You need to upload a large number of files to a single location after the workspace runs.
Your workspace concludes by making an HTTP POST call with a JSON body.
